      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve honestly babied this car since day one, and it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a dent anywhere, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
