    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 represents the pinnacle of rotary performance, featuring a 13B-REW engine with verified high-compression rotors and a perfectly calibrated sequential twin-turbocharger system. The factory-spec vacuum routing has been meticulously refreshed to ensure seamless boost transition. The chassis is exceptional, retaining its original double-wishbone geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential with no signs of subframe oxidation. Thermal management is optimized via a multi-core aluminum radiator and upgraded oil coolers. The exterior retains its original high-gloss finish with consistent paint depth and all factory VIN tags present. Inside, the cockpit is flawless, with no dash lift or bolster wear, reflecting a truly preserved, collector-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
