    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a high-end ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, scratches, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory scent persists. Every button, screen, and electronic driver-assist system functions flawlessly, exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a complete, chronologically organized service history included. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover, never seen inclement weather, and has been a non-smoker, pet-free environment since day one. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually untouched specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
